      <th style="padding:10px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; text-align:left;">English</th>
      <th style="padding:10px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; text-align:left;">When to Use</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">多少钱？</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">duōshǎo qián?</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">How much?</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Any purchase</td></tr>
    <tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">我要这个</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">wǒ yào zhège</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">I want this one</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Pointing at items</td></tr>
    <tr><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">我看看</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">wǒ kànkan</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">I'm just looking</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">When browsing</td></tr>
    <tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">有没有…？</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">yǒu méiyǒu…?</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Do you have…?</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Looking for something</td></tr>
    <tr><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">可以看一下吗？</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">kěyǐ kàn yīxià ma?</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Can I take a look?</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Items behind counter</td></tr>
    <tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">买单 / 结账</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">mǎidān / jiézhàng</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Check please / pay</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Ready to pay</td></tr>
